Class ExtensionData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.skylark.parser.ExtensionData

  • @ParametersAreNonnullByDefault
 @Generated(value="org.immutables.processor.ProxyProcessor")
 @Immutable
 @CheckReturnValue
public final class ExtensionData
extends Object
    Captures Extension and information related to its parsing like all other extensions used in order to load it. The main purpose of extra information is to properly captured all dependent information for caching purposes.
